data.description: Come see this unique opportunity to own a meticulously maintained beautifully renovated double wide manufactured home, on land that you own! Gull Aire Village is registered with the State of Florida as a 55+ community. Monthly assessments only $50! It's like you're on vacation every day! Pool, Spa, Bocce Ball, Club House and more! Bring your pet! This is a corner unit with the side covered parking that is adjacent to nature. Beautiful kitchen featuring Shaker style cabinets, granite counters, upgraded flooring, renovated bathrooms paint and more! Primary suite features a full bathroom. Enclosed bonus room with separate entrance. Additional screened in porch area, and last but not least,  room to sit under the large covered space over the driveway facing the nature with a small patio.  Room to park two cars. Best of all, the location is prime! This property is located in highly sought after Oldsmar and is close to Tampa Bay, beaches, downtown, shopping and all that Tampa has to offer! Close proximity to both Tampa airports. Come get it while it lasts!
